<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:12
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1365' id='t-1365'>I want to start with a game. Okay?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='4015' id='t-4015'>And to win this game,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='6434' id='t-6434'>all you have to do is see
