<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='9347' id='t-9347'>as it really is, all right?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='11363' id='t-11363'>So we have two panels here,
of colored dots.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='14846' id='t-14846'>And one of those dots
is the same in the two panels.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='21370' id='t-21370'>And you have to tell me which one.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:34
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='23442' id='t-23442'>Now, I narrowed it down</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='24914' id='t-24914'>to the gray one, the green one,
and, say, the orange one.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='29609' id='t-29609'>So by a show of hands,
we'll start with the easiest one.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='32696' id='t-32696'>Show of hands: how many people
