<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='36434' id='t-36434'>Really? Okay.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='38000' id='t-38000'>How many people think it's the green one?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='42577' id='t-42577'>And how many people
think it's the orange one?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='46875' id='t-46875'>Pretty even split.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:01
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='50323' id='t-50323'>Let's find out what the reality is.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='52614' id='t-52614'>Here is the orange one.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:06
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='55713' id='t-55713'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:09
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='58000' id='t-58000'>Here is the green one.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='61212' id='t-61212'>And here is the gray one.</span>
