<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='64712' id='t-64712'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:19
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='68000' id='t-68000'>So for all of you who saw that,
you're complete realists.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='71268' id='t-71268'>All right?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:23
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='72465' id='t-72465'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:25
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='74000' id='t-74000'>So this is pretty amazing, isn't it?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='75795' id='t-75795'>Because nearly every living system</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='77621' id='t-77621'>has evolved the ability
