<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='85752' id='t-85752'>And yet, even at this
most fundamental level,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='88577' id='t-88577'>context is everything.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='91220' id='t-91220'>What I'm going to talk about
